name: Angie Nelson
description: I am kind, sincere, full of energy, active, goal-oriented, persistent, charismatic and cheerful. I influence other people positively, they say I am like sunshine. I always cheer up and encourage others. I take my life positively, everything is working only for my best! I believe that positive attitude can help to solve a lot of problems. I never get upset about small things but try look ahead and keep on moving.
